Choose a planfor your needs

Choose a plan for your needs

Plan 1

Start-up consultation (90 min)

  • In-depth questionnaire completed in advance
  • 3 day diet plan completed in advance
  • Review of your situation, health history, diet, lifestyle
  • Assessment of current health status based on charts and symptoms
  • Recommendation for the purchase of relevant nutrition-related laboratory tests, if necessary
  • Measuring and weighing body composition (if applicable)
  • Blood pressure measurement (if applicable)

1675 DKK

Plan 2

Test and follow-up consultation (15 + 60 min)

  • Testing and guidance
  • Review of laboratory analysis/tests
  • Planning a diet adapted to your test results
  • Vitamin and dietary supplement recommendations
  • In-depth questionnaire completed in advance
  • Review of your situation, health history, diet, lifestyle
  • Measuring and weighing body composition (if applicable)
  • Blood pressure measurement (if applicable)

1175 DKK

Plan3

Full starter pack

  • Start-up consultation with Kristine or Bianca (90 min)
  • 1 x Follow-up consultation (60 min)
  • 1 x Final consultation (60 min)
  • In-depth questionnaire completed in advance
  • Diet registration
  • Vitamin and dietary supplement recommendations
  • Relevant blood tests or other laboratory tests can be purchased additionally by agreement
  • Planning and guidance for a personalized 2-week meal plan

3800 DKK

What our clients say

What our clients say

Malena, 43
Thank you, Health Clinic!

l was recommended to a course with Kristine. Following her advice about diet, lifestyle and nutritional supplements has meant that I live almost completely without headaches and have more energy.

I have gone from having headaches almost every day to knowing my body is reacting to eating gluten. I can therefore control it myself now based on what I put in my body. Kristine is now only a call or email away and she always answers and is ready to help if I need support and help

7 Days Ago
Maria, 31
Finally living pain free

I struggle with very painful and irregular periods and cramps and feel sick whole week during my period.

Through Health Clinic I figured out I have endometriosis and learnt how to cope better during those days. I never thought of how specific foods worsen my condition and how tender movement could actually improve my cramps and energy levels. I also am more aware of my cycle now and get to plan in advance how to prepare myself for my periods by organizing my diet.

10.04.2018
Louise, 52
Source to gain holistic knowledge

Ive always searched for holistic ways to balance my mind and body, therefore the Health Clinic looked like a place that could help me out.

After booking my first appointment I received an email with questionnarie. In this way, already on my first consultation I felt all attention was on me. Through all the process after tests and treatments I got to learn a lot about women's natural cycles and understand that we don't need to experience these horrible hot flashes or mood swings during menopause. We need to know our own body, hormones and how our lifestyle influences our health.

5 Month Ago
